<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714453495426031705.png" title="1714453495426031705.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">为进一步规范我校学生的文明行为、加强对学生日常仪容仪表的管理，培养学生良好的行为习惯，创建积极向上、文明和谐的学习环境，将学雷锋的种子播撒在我院每位学子心中，<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">4</span>月<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">15</span>日，经济管理学院“啄木鸟”专项行动正式开始。“啄木鸟”志愿者轮流站岗，共同维护校园环境。此次活动分为两个点位，一是茶百道门店<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">T</span>字路口处，二是篮球场旁的十字路口处。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714456086724055150.png" title="1714456086724055150.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">（啄木鸟志愿者站岗 曾文洁 摄）</span></p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">“啄木鸟”志愿者们主要负责维护校园秩序，面对乱扔垃圾、乱说脏话、随地吐痰、路上吸烟等不文明行为及时进行制止和劝导，不仅维护了校园的良好教学环境，同时也让同学们认识到不文明行为对校园产生的负面影响，并为创建美丽校园贡献自己的一份力量。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714455994484043776.png" title="1714455994484043776.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">（啄木鸟志愿者站岗 郭毓 摄）</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;">志愿者们分组驻守在各自岗位，制止校园不文明行为、主动捡起地上的垃圾。每个志愿者都坚守岗位，各司其职，不怕苦不怕累，彰显了新时代青年大学生应有的风采。</span><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714456211809068220.png" title="1714456211809068220.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.38em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">啄木鸟志愿者劝导行人垃圾入袋&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.38em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（郭毓 摄）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.38em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714456238649051371.png" title="1714456238649051371.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 39.857px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 2.08em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-si